title: Jungle/Top Main Looking for team
body:
Finished my placement games and was placed in bronze 2 as my first season in ranked and from there have dropped, i personally think i'm atleast a silver player so yeah just looking for some players to team up with to climb the ranks together, just send friend request or message me if you're keen.

Summoner Name: Slammoth

replies.body: Im a jg main and would love to join an active team. Im a Silver 1. Not sure about your match history... :/
